card_text:
(The tide is low.)
The cost for the Keyraken to advance is 
3A per player.
Omni: Your team loses a total of 2A
per player as a group. If you do, raise 
the tide.
(The tide is high.)
The cost for the Keyraken to advance is 
6A per player.
After the Keyraken advances, lower 
the tide.
flavor_text:
As long as the Keyraken must fight the current, 
perhaps there is a chance.
